'''''Star Wars: The Official Magazine'' 46''', also styled as '''''Star Wars'' Magazine 46''',  was the 46th issue of the ''[[Star Wars: The Official Magazine]]'', released on [[August 21]], [[2003]]. It primarily reprinted content from [[Star Wars Insider 66|''Star Wars Insider'' 66]].

